<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Personal Portfolio: Professional Trader Trainer</title>
    <style>
        :root { --dark-bg: #121212; --dark-surface: #1e1e1e; --accent-purple: #9c27b0; --accent-gold: #ffc107; --text-light: #e0e0e0; }
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background-color: var(--dark-bg); color: var(--text-light); margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
        nav { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; background: rgba(18,18,18,0.9); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 5%; z-index: 100; align-items: center; }
        .logo-nav { height: 40px; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px var(--accent-purple)); }
        #hero { height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0 10%; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; text-align: center; }
        .hero-img { width: 250px; height: 250px; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid var(--accent-purple); object-fit: cover; }
        .btn-gold { background: var(--accent-gold); color: #111; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 15px; }
        #gallery { padding: 50px 10%; background: var(--dark-surface); }
        .gallery-item { margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
        .gallery-item img { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <img src="logo.jpg" alt="Logo" class="logo-nav">
        <div style="font-weight: bold;">TRADER TRAINER</div>
    </nav>

    <section id="hero">
        <img src="wajah.jpg" alt="Wajah Saya" class="hero-img">
        <div>
            <h1>Mastering Markets from Minimalist Space</h1>
            <p>Disiplin, Data, dan Mindset Professional Trading.</p>
            <a href="#gallery" class="btn-gold">Lihat Setup Saya</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery">
        <div class="gallery-item">
            <h3>The Practitioner's Lab</h3>
            <img src="keahlian.jpg" alt="Trading Setup">
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
            <h3>Focus & Discipline Zone</h3>
            <img src="keahlian anlisia.jpg" alt="Focus Zone">
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #666;">
        &copy; 2026 Professional Trader Portfolio
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
